    <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">Version 1.0 Summer Release!</h2>
    <p>
      The first official version of Spark Design System includes two Spark packages. The Spark-Core package includes
      components that are the basic building blocks of an application. Spark-Extras are
      components that may not be needed by all applications, but are consistent with the style of Spark-Core
    </p>

    <p class="sprk-u-mbs">
      The following components are available in
      <a class="drizzle-b-Link drizzle-b-Label" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sparkdesignsystem/spark-core">Spark-Core</a>:
    </p>

    <div class="drizzle-u-Columned sprk-u-mbm">
      <ul class="drizzle-b-List drizzle-b-List--spacing-s drizzle-b-List--nested">
        <li>Accordions</li>
        <li>Alerts</li>
        <li>Buttons</li>
        <li>Dividers</li>
        <li>Footer</li>
        <li>Icons</li>
        <li>Inputs</li>
        <li>Links</li>
        <li>Lists</li>
        <li>Masthead</li>
        <li>Modals</li>
        <li>Navigation</li>
        <li>Pagination</li>
        <li>Promo</li>
        <li>Tables</li>
        <li>Tabbed Navigation</li>
        <li>Toggle</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="sprk-u-mbs">
      The following components are available in
      <a class="drizzle-b-Link drizzle-b-Label" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sparkdesignsystem/spark-extras">Spark-Extras</a>:
    </p>

    <div class="drizzle-u-Columned">
      <ul class="drizzle-b-List drizzle-b-List--spacing-s drizzle-b-List--nested">
        <li>Card</li>
        <li>Dictionary</li>
        <li>Highlight Board</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
