  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
      Updates From Beta to v1
    </h2>

    <ul class="drizzle-b-List drizzle-b-List--nested">
      <li>
        Updated the typography sizes and line heights.
      </li>

      <li>
        Reduced the heading type sizes to six and removed '.sprk-b-TypeDisplaySeven'.
      </li>

      <li>
        Updated Spark-Core, Spark-Extras and Spark Site unit test coverage to 100%.
      </li>

      <li>
        Updated the heading colors of the category titles
        in the side navigation of the Spark Site.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added more useful explainer content for components.
      </li>

      <li>
        Fixed an issue in the Navigation component where long
        navigation items were breaking out of their container instead of wrapping.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added two example pages to the Spark test pages.
      </li>

      <li>
        Removed some npm packages from Spark-Extras components that were not needed.
      </li>

      <li>
        Accessibility updates to add screen reader text to the hamburger icon.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added a JS timer to close the Wait Modal component for
        the Spark Site documentation so users don't have to refresh the page.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added CODEOWNERS file to specify the Spark team as owners.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added contribution and bug report GitHub issue templates.
      </li>

      <li>
        Fixed an error in the '.sprk-is-Disabled' class name for
        Buttons where it was incorrectly named as '.is-Disabled'.
      </li>

      <li>
        Added a section to the Spark Site for z-indexes called Layers.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
